      "Error policy decisions are distributed per subsystem instead of encoded in shared primitives.",
      "Startup policy metadata (`required`/`optional`) is not consistently enforced by step implementations.",
      "Resource lifecycle conventions for docker clients are duplicated and unevenly adopted."
    ],
    "likely_symptoms": [
      "background_loop_failure_policy_drift",
      "required_callback_contract_bypassed",
      "docker_client_close_handling_inconsistent"
    ],
